&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generous Paid Time Off – starting with up to 144 hours of vacation, 40 hours of sick time, 13 Company paid holidays, a birthday holiday, and 2 floating holidays per calendar year.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Health Benefits – benefit eligible on 1&lt;sup&gt;st&lt;/sup&gt; day, 100% paid for employee and 90% paid for family coverage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401 (k) with company match up to 6%&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;16 weeks of paid parental leave&lt;/li&gt;
